data.description: Live in the heart of Gilbert in this turnkey impeccably maintained home! You can feel the warmth as soon as you drive up because it's been LOVED! ALL the important updates have been completed. Carpets, ceiling fans (2023,). Roof underlayment, windows, toilets, kitchen gas range, microwave, washer/dryer (2022). Garage door, water filtration system (2020). Tuff shed, window shades, house paint, patio solar shade, HVAC, ext house paint (2019). Dishwasher & fridge (2018). See entire list of updates in the Documents Tab. Open floor plan boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, 2 car garage. Mature shade trees front & back w/fruit-bearing trees. 5 mins from San Tan Mall, Costco, 202 freeway & many excellent restaurants. Gilbert Regional Park w/sport courts, pickleball, lake & splash pad. Welcome Home! :-)
